---
alwaysApply: true
---

Run console PHP, npm and npx command via `docker exec -i repair_service_app <any commands>`

If editing is not possible, run the command `docker exec -i repair_service_app chmod -R 777 ./`

In the controller, implement all logic in a separate Service class.

To output Model data, always use Resource.

To implement filtering, study the files in the [Filters] fi (./app/Filters/).

Always use ziggy vue. After creating and renaming of route run `php artisan ziggy:generate --types`
